OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1774361471
OL,3,CFirst Minecraft theme park land to
OL,4,Copen in London next year
OL,6,FThe world's first Minecraft theme park
OL,7,Fland is set to open in the UK in 2027
OL,8,Fand plans to bring the bestselling
OL,9,Fvideo game of all time to life.
OL,11,FMinecraft World will open at
OL,12,FChessington World of Adventures in
OL,13,Fsouth-west London and with the world's
OL,14,Ffirst Minecraft-themed rollercoaster,
OL,15,Fas well as themed shops and dining.
OL,17,FFans will be able to go on interactive
OL,18,Fadventures and explore block built
OL,19,Fplayscapes in a world inspired by
OL,20,FMinecraft's most popular biomes, mobs
OL,21,Fand items, developers say.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/6
