OL,3,CFirst Minecraft theme park land to
OL,4,Copen in London next year
OL,6,FThe #50 million project is a
OL,7,Fcollaboration between Merlin
OL,8,FEntertainments, the owner of Legoland,
OL,9,FAlton Towers and Thorpe Park, and
OL,10,FMojang Studios, the company behind
OL,11,FMinecraft.
OL,13,FMinecraft creators ` including
OL,14,FYouTubers Grian, Aimsey, DanTDM, and
OL,15,FLDShadowLady ` will work with Merlin
OL,16,Fand Mojang to come up with ideas for
OL,17,Fthe development.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/6
