PN,40803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1774361471
OL,3,CFirst Minecraft theme park land to
OL,4,Copen in London next year
OL,6,FAngela Jobson, senior vice president
OL,7,Fof global brand at Merlin
OL,8,FEntertainments said: "We're absolutely
OL,9,Fthrilled to be bringing Minecraft's
OL,10,Fcreativity, bold adventures, and
OL,11,Fridiculous fun to life at a theme park
OL,12,Ffor the first time at Chessington
OL,13,FWorld of Adventures.
OL,26,@pD@VOU
