OL,3,CFirst Minecraft theme park land to
OL,4,Copen in London next year
OL,6,F"Minecraft World will allow friends
OL,7,Fand families to play, explore and
OL,8,Fcraft together on a truly epic scale.
OL,9,FWorking closely together with Mojang
OL,10,FStudios we are meticulously creating
OL,11,Fan authentic world that the global
OL,12,Fcommunity of Minecraft fans will want
OL,13,Fto immerse themselves in and
OL,14,Fexperience the game in a whole new
OL,15,Fway."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@EO]
