OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1774361471
OL,3,CFirst Minecraft theme park land to
OL,4,Copen in London next year
OL,6,FTorfi Frans Olafsson, senior creative
OL,7,Fdirector of entertainment at Minecraft
OL,8,Fsaid: "Minecraft World represents a
OL,9,Fmeaningful milestone in our ongoing
OL,10,Fjourney to expand the Minecraft
OL,11,Funiverse.
OL,13,F"We're thrilled to have partnered with
OL,14,FMerlin Entertainments to realise a
OL,15,Fplace where you can literally be in
OL,16,Fthe Minecraft Overworld and have an
OL,17,Fadventure of your own with your family
OL,18,Fand friends.
OL,26,@pD@GOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/6
