PN,40806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1774361471
OL,3,CFirst Minecraft theme park land to
OL,4,Copen in London next year
OL,6,F"The team at Merlin Entertainments and
OL,7,FMojang have worked hard to craft an
OL,8,Fexperience that feels immersive,
OL,9,Fauthentic and welcoming, and we can't
OL,10,Fwait for our community to experience
OL,11,Fit."
OL,13,FMinecraft is the bestselling video
OL,14,Fgame of all time, with millions of
OL,15,Fpeople playing every day.
OL,17,FThe block-building video game has
OL,18,Fpreviously been adapted into a film
OL,19,Fcalled A Minecraft Movie which was the
OL,20,Fhighest grossing film at the box
OL,21,Foffice in the UK and Ireland in 2025.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@DO]
